### Payment Verification API Tests

### 1. Create Payment Intent (with provider)
POST http://localhost:8084/payments/intents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "orderId": "order-456",
  "amount": 99.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Test payment for order",
  "provider": "STRIPE"
}

### 2. Verify Payment (checks provider and verifies with Stripe)
POST http://localhost:8084/payments/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "order-456",
  "paymentIntentId": "pi_test_123456789"
}

### 3. Get Payment Intent Details
GET http://localhost:8084/payments/intents/pi_test_123456789
